data.description: What a great location across from the community park with a pool! Well maintained home with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a 1 car attached garage. Large fenced yard on a corner lot with great mountain views and RV parking. Home does need some cosmetic work but is move-in ready with stainless steel appliances and a fully finished basement. Easy access to military bases, downtown, shopping, and restaurants.
